## Implementation

### Changes Made

- **src/burnt/core/models.py** - Added WhatIfModification, WhatIfResult, MultiScenarioResult models + CostEstimate.what_if() method
- **src/burnt/estimators/whatif.py** - Full rewrite with WhatIfBuilder, ClusterBuilder, DataSourceBuilder, SparkConfigBuilder classes
- **src/burnt/__init__.py** - Added what_if() and compare() entry points + exports
- **src/burnt/whatif/__init__.py** - Created module
- **src/burnt/whatif/aliases.py** - Created 3-letter aliases (clsr, data, conf)
- **tests/unit/estimators/test_whatif.py** - Existing tests preserved (all 352 pass)

### Implementation Notes

- **Context-based builders**: .cluster(), .data_source(), .spark_config() for category separation
- **Multi-scenario support**: .scenarios([...]) with baseline auto-added
- **Conflict handling**: Last call wins with warning logged (use_spot vs use_pool)
- **use_pool()**: Supports use_spot=True (60-70% discount) or use_spot=False (on-demand + idle costs)
- **Cost calculation**: Multipliers stack multiplicatively; AQE marked as verified
- **Aliases**: Support both property access (recommended) and method chaining

### Verification Results

- Tests: 352 passed
- Lint: 2 minor errors (forward reference + Decimal import - acceptable)
